What you need to know:

He revealed that Gor Mahia needs Sh4 million to cater for travelling logistics and accommodation among other pertinent issues. Oruo said the  club has written to the Ministry of Sports through the Football Kenya Federation seeking for financial aid to raise the amount.The record champions preparation for the match has however been hampered by go slow with players demanding their pay for last month while others who were in the last season  squad  are demanding salary arrears accrued before.